---
syntax: bash
tags: [ sort, ]
---
explanation: sort - sort lines of text files
 
# To sort a file:
sort file

# To sort a file by keeping only unique:
sort -u file

# To sort a file and reverse the result:
sort -r file

# To sort a file randomly:
sort -R file

# To sort 3rd column with : seperated
sort -t : -k 3n
